sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant H as Human / Sender
    participant G as AXME Cloud Runtime
    participant T as Tool System
    participant AG as Agent System
    participant S as Internal Scheduler

    Note over G: Intent enters WAITING state

    alt WAITING_FOR_HUMAN
        H  ->> G: POST /resume (approve or continue)
    else WAITING_FOR_TOOL
        T -->> G: tool result event
    else WAITING_FOR_AGENT
        AG -->> G: continuation callback
    else WAITING_FOR_TIME
        S -->> G: wakeup at next_wakeup_at
    end

    G ->> G: re-evaluate workflow step

    alt condition satisfied
        G -->> H: state → IN_PROGRESS
    else still blocked
        G ->> S: schedule next wakeup
        G -->> H: remains WAITING
    end
